OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777921886
OL,3,CDrivers protest over toll bridge fine
OL,4,Cconfusion
OL,6,FLocal drivers are protesting after
OL,7,Freceiving surprise fines, months after
OL,8,Fthey crossed a toll bridge.
OL,10,FThe fee to cross Warburton Toll
OL,11,FBridge, near Lymm, went up from 12p to
OL,12,F#1 in December, when an online payment
OL,13,Fsystem was introduced.
OL,15,FBut some drivers say they have been
OL,16,Fsurprised with fines up to five months
OL,17,Fafter they crossed the bridge.
OL,19,FRachel Alexander has received multiple
OL,20,Ffines from crossing the bridge,
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777921886
OL,3,CDrivers protest over toll bridge fine
OL,4,Cconfusion
OL,6,FShe said: "I paid five so far, but I
OL,7,Fwas getting more and more which made
OL,8,Fme realise something wasn't right.
OL,10,F"I think it's rubbish. I think they're
OL,11,Ftrying to use the computer and relying
OL,12,Fon that, and the computer is not up to
OL,13,Fstandard."
OL,15,FDrivers are asked to pay the #1 toll
OL,16,Fonline by midnight the day after they
OL,17,Fuse the bridge, with automatic number
OL,18,Fplate recognition (ANPR) cameras
OL,19,Fmonitoring the crossing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
