PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777921886
OL,3,CDrivers protest over toll bridge fine
OL,4,Cconfusion
OL,6,FRegular users can set up a pre-paid
OL,7,Faccount for the tolls to be taken
OL,8,Fautomatically, with discounts for
OL,9,Flocal residents or Blue Badge holders.
OL,11,FThose who fail to pay are sent an
OL,12,FUnpaid Toll Charge letter, and can
OL,13,Fface fines of up to #100.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Manchester Ship
OL,16,FCanal Company said: "This is a
OL,17,Fsignificant modernisation of the
OL,18,Fbridge operation and an adjustment for
OL,19,Fusers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
