OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777921886
OL,3,CDrivers protest over toll bridge fine
OL,4,Cconfusion
OL,6,F"The approach we are taking on
OL,7,Fenforcement is proportionate and fair
OL,8,Fas it balances the responsibility we
OL,9,Fhave to drivers who have paid the
OL,10,Ftolls, or those who have only had
OL,11,Fminor missed payments."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
